==Burying the bones==
===Outside Yu'biusk===
* {{mes|You should go to Yu'biusk before you bury this bone.}}
* {{tact|end}}

===In Yu'biusk===
* {{mes|You dig a hole in the ground...}}
* {{mes|You bury the bones and feel a wave of gratitude from the spirit of [high priest].}}
* {{tact|end}}

